OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,FInspectors visited the County Durham
OL,7,Fand Darlington NHS Foundation Trust's
OL,8,Fsites following a warning notice
OL,9,Fissued by the CQC after its previous
OL,10,Finspection in March last year.
OL,12,FThe latest inspection, in January, was
OL,13,Fan unannounced visit to both units
OL,14,Fduring which the CQC judged the
OL,15,Fhospitals had met the terms of the
OL,16,Fwarning notice, which has now been
OL,17,Fremoved.
OL,19,FDespite improvements, the CQC found
OL,20,Fthe trust needed to continue to
OL,21,Fimprove in a number of areas.
