OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,FIt said that although there was now a
OL,7,Fprocess for documenting arrival times
OL,8,Ffor those attending triage, new
OL,9,Fsystems within the triage unit were
OL,10,Fnot yet fully embedded.
OL,12,FIt was also found that staff did not
OL,13,Falways complete environmental and
OL,14,Femergency equipment safety checks in
OL,15,Faccordance with the trust policy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
