OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,FFinally, staff did not always ensure
OL,7,Fmedicines and sterile consumable items
OL,8,Fwere always stored, managed, and
OL,9,Freplaced before their expiry dates.
OL,10,FThis was not in accordance with the
OL,11,Ftrust's policy and best practice
OL,12,Fguidance.
OL,14,FLinda Hirst, CQC deputy director of
OL,15,Foperations for the north, said:
OL,16,F"Leaders were now more visible and
OL,17,Fapproachable for staff, and a new
OL,18,Fdirector of midwifery had been
OL,19,Fappointed, therefore we expect to see
OL,20,Ffurther improvements next time we
OL,21,Fvisit.
