OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,F"We found improvements with the
OL,7,Fmanagement of incidents. For example,
OL,8,Fwe reviewed four serious incidents and
OL,9,Ffound the service now implemented much
OL,10,Fbetter action plans in response to
OL,11,Finvestigating findings.
OL,13,F"This ensured lessons were learnt and
OL,14,Fwomen, people using the service and
OL,15,Ftheir babies were receiving safer care
OL,16,Fas a result."
