OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,FShe continued: "There had also been
OL,7,Fsome improvements around staffing and
OL,8,Fongoing recruitment. However, both
OL,9,Fservices didn't always have enough
OL,10,Fsenior, experienced midwives on labour
OL,11,Fwards which needs to be addressed as a
OL,12,Fpriority.
OL,14,F"We did have some other areas of
OL,15,Fconcern including timely inductions of
OL,16,Flabour to meet people's needs, which
OL,17,Fweren't always happening at either
OL,18,Fhospital. Although oversight of these
OL,19,Fdelays had improved, new processes put
OL,20,Fin place to improve them weren't fully
OL,21,Fembedded yet."
