OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,FThe CQC added that staff had clearly
OL,7,Fworked hard since their inspection in
OL,8,FMarch 2023, and they know further
OL,9,Fimprovements were needed.
OL,11,FImprovements found at both hospitals:
OL,13,FAs well as maternity services, the
OL,14,Frating for how safe and well-led the
OL,15,Fservices were for both University
OL,16,FHospital of North Durham and
OL,17,FDarlington Memorial Hospital had
OL,18,Fimproved from inadequate to requires
OL,19,Fimprovement.
