OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,FIt means the overall rating for both
OL,7,Fhospitals has improved from requires
OL,8,Fimprovement to good. It means the
OL,9,Ftrust remains rated as good overall.
OL,11,FThe County Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust will continue to be
OL,13,Fmonitored through future inspections.
OL,15,FThe trust said: "The new rating is a
OL,16,Fpositive step forward on its
OL,17,Fcontinuing improvement journey and
OL,18,Fthat it will use feedback to work
OL,19,Ftowards future improvements.
