OL,3,C'Inadequate' maternity services at two
OL,4,CCounty Durham hospitals improve
OL,6,F"The new rating is a positive step
OL,7,Fforward, and our dedicated teams have
OL,8,Fimplemented robust measures to enhance
OL,9,Fthe safety, quality, and experience of
OL,10,Four maternity services.
OL,12,F"We remain fully aware that there is
OL,13,Fstill work to be done and have already
OL,14,Fbegun to deliver on an action plan
OL,15,Fwith defined timescales and measurable
OL,16,Fimprovements.
OL,18,F"Our aim is to ensure that every
OL,19,Ffamily feels supported, empowered, and
OL,20,Fsafe throughout their maternity
OL,21,Fjourney."
